<text id="02-output-contract" title="RAG Policy Thresholds Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for `RAGPolicy` — numeric thresholds per signal + default action per colour + evidence + owner + refresh cadence.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/rag-policy.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["project_id", "header", "signals", "actions", "review_log"],
  "properties": {
    "project_id": {"type": "string"},
    "header": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["owner", "last_reviewed", "version", "trigger", "reporting_cadence_days"],
      "properties": {
        "owner": {"type": "object", "required": ["role", "person"], "properties": {"role": {"type": "string"}, "person": {"type": "string", "minLength": 2}}},
        "last_reviewed": {"type": "string", "format": "date"},
        "version": {"type": "string"},
        "trigger": {"enum": ["weekly_status", "fortnightly_status", "monthly_status"]},
        "reporting_cadence_days": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 30}
      }
    },
    "signals": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["signal_id", "input_source", "amber_threshold", "red_threshold", "comparator", "evidence"],
        "properties": {
          "signal_id": {"type": "string"},
          "input_source": {"type": "string"},
          "amber_threshold": {"type": "number"},
          "red_threshold": {"type": "number"},
          "comparator": {"enum": ["gt", "lt", "gte", "lte", "eq"]},
          "evidence": {"type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": {"type": "string"}}
        }
      }
    },
    "actions": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["green", "amber", "red"],
      "properties": {
        "green": {"type": "string"},
        "amber": {"type": "string", "minLength": 10},
        "red": {"type": "string", "minLength": 10}
      }
    },
    "review_log": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "required": ["reviewed_at"]}}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>`signals[*].amber_threshold` or `red_threshold` non-numeric ("significant", "material") — violates `r2-bounded-output`.</item>
      <item>`actions.red` empty or generic "discuss" — violates `r4-named-owner`.</item>
      <item>`header.last_reviewed` &gt; 90 days — violates `r5-iteration-loop`.</item>
      <item>`signals[*].evidence` empty — violates `r3-evidence-anchored`.</item>
      <item>`header.trigger` "when_needed" — violates `r1-explicit-trigger`.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "project_id": "checkout",
  "header": {"owner": {"role": "PM", "person": "pm-handle"}, "last_reviewed": "2026-05-10", "version": "1.4", "trigger": "weekly_status", "reporting_cadence_days": 7},
  "signals": [
    {"signal_id": "schedule_variance_pct", "input_source": "Jira velocity report", "amber_threshold": 10, "red_threshold": 20, "comparator": "gt",
     "evidence": ["incident-2025-Q4-acme-overrun", "policy://pmo/schedule-tolerance"]},
    {"signal_id": "defect_escape_rate", "input_source": "Sentry weekly export", "amber_threshold": 0.05, "red_threshold": 0.10, "comparator": "gt",
     "evidence": ["postmortem-2026-Q1"]}
  ],
  "actions": {"green": "continue normal cadence", "amber": "PM scheduled mid-week health-check; surface in next sync", "red": "fire distressed-project-rescue playbook; sponsor notified within 4h"},
  "review_log": [{"reviewed_at": "2026-05-10"}]
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "project_id": "x",
  "header": {"owner": {"role": "team", "person": ""}, "last_reviewed": "2024-01-01", "version": "0", "trigger": "when_needed", "reporting_cadence_days": 7},
  "signals": [{"signal_id": "schedule", "input_source": "guess", "amber_threshold": "significant", "red_threshold": "material", "comparator": "gt", "evidence": []}],
  "actions": {"green": "", "amber": "discuss", "red": "..."},
  "review_log": []
}
]]></code>
    <note>Non-numeric thresholds; no evidence; vague trigger; empty owner; actions too short.</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-rag-policy-thresholds.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
